  <summary date="2021-07-27T10:59:20Z" status="Introduced in House">Reducing Exposure to Burn Pits Act

This bill requires the Department of Defense (DOD) to provide budget information regarding incinerators and waste-to-energy waste disposal alternatives to burn pits. DOD must include the information as a dedicated budget line item in the President's FY2022 budget.</summary>
